50|$|Two <b>Zener</b> <b>diodes</b> {{facing each}} other in series will act to clip both halves of an input signal. Waveform {{clippers}} can be used not only to reshape a signal, but also to prevent voltage spikes from affecting circuits that {{are connected to the}} power supply.|$|R
